headline: SK hynix First to Complete Intel Data Center Certification for 32Gb Die-based 256GB Server DDR5 RDIMM
summary: SK hynix Inc. (or "the company", www.skhynix.com) announced today that it has become the first in the industry to complete the Intel Data Center Certified process to apply 256GB DDR5 RDIMM[1]—a high capacity server module based on 32Gb fifth-generation 10nm-class (1b) DRAM— to Intel® Xeon® 6 platform.
